# File: app/assets/css/font-awesome.min.css.ab
# Purpose: Font Awesome 4.6.3 icon font CSS — minified copy loaded by the application from app/assets/css/
# Dependencies: []

## Overview
Minified copy of Font Awesome 4.6.3 CSS (4 lines). Provides the FontAwesome icon glyph font and all `.fa`/`.fa-*` utility classes used throughout the TuyoTools UI. References font files at `../fonts/fontawesome-webfont.*`.

## Interface
No exports. Loaded as a `<link>` stylesheet in `app/index.html`.

## Dependencies
No project-level dependencies. Vendor file. Requires font files at `app/assets/fonts/fontawesome-webfont.{eot,woff2,woff,ttf,svg}`.

## Implementation Notes
- Font Awesome version: 4.6.3 (Font: SIL OFL 1.1, CSS: MIT License, @davegandy)
- 4 lines minified
- Defines `@font-face` for the FontAwesome glyph font
- Includes all icon classes and modifier classes (`.fa-spin`, `.fa-fw`, `.fa-lg`, `.fa-2x`–`.fa-5x`, `.fa-rotate-*`, `.fa-flip-*`, `.fa-stack`, etc.)
- Same content as `app/styles/font-awesome.min.css`
